@startuml contract-architecture
title PaymentSplitter Contract — Architecture

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam classBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
skinparam classBorderColor #4CAF50

class PaymentSplitter {
  -- Storage --
  + owner: address
  + platformFee: uint256  // basis points, e.g. 50 = 0.5%
  + developers: mapping(address => Developer)
  + usedTxSigs: mapping(bytes32 => bool)
  + usdcToken: IERC20

  -- Developer Registry --
  + register(wallet: address): void
  + isRegistered(wallet: address): bool

  -- Payment --
  + pay(developerId: address, amount: uint256, txSig: bytes32): void
  + getBalance(developer: address): uint256

  -- Withdrawal --
  + withdraw(amount: uint256): void
  + withdrawAll(): void

  -- Admin --
  + setFee(bps: uint256): void  // owner only
  + withdrawPlatformFees(): void // owner only
}

class Developer {
  + wallet: address
  + balance: uint256
  + registeredAt: uint256
  + totalReceived: uint256
}

class "Middleware\n(off-chain)" as MW {
  + withPaywall(handler, opts): Handler
  -- opts --
  + price: string     // "$0.01"
  + developerId: address
  + network: string   // "arc-mainnet" | "arc-testnet"
}

class "AI Agent\n(buyer)" as Agent {
  + GatewayClient or own x402 impl
  + USDC balance on Arc
}

Agent --> PaymentSplitter : pay(developerId, amount, txSig)
PaymentSplitter --> Developer : credit balance\n(amount - platformFee%)
MW ..> PaymentSplitter : verify tx onchain
MW ..> Agent : 402 with payment requirements
Agent ..> MW : retry with X-Payment header

note bottom of PaymentSplitter
  Deployed once by platform.
  All developers share one contract.
  Platform fee changeable by owner only.
  Replay protection via usedTxSigs mapping.
end note

@enduml
